# Dotfiles: diretórios e arquivos que são symlinks para o repositório de dotfiles

Legenda: `origem → symlink → destino real`

## Principais links

| Path | Link | Destino real |
|------|------|-------------|
| ~/.agents/ | → ~/_Dev/dotfiles/data/.agents/ | → ~/dotfiles/data/.agents/ |
| ~/.zshrc | → ~/dotfiles/data/.zshrc | |
| ~/.zsh/ | → ~/_Dev/dotfiles/data/.zsh/ | → ~/dotfiles/data/.zsh/ |
| ~/.tmux.conf | → ~/_Dev/dotfiles/data/.tmux.conf | → ~/dotfiles/data/.tmux.conf |
| ~/.gitconfig | → ~/dotfiles/data/gitconfig | |
| ~/.config/kdeglobals | → ~/dotfiles/data/kde-plasma/.config/kdeglobals | |
| ~/.config/kwinrc | → ~/dotfiles/data/kde-plasma/.config/kwinrc | |
| ~/.config/kwinrulesrc | → ~/dotfiles/data/kde-plasma/.config/kwinrulesrc | |
| ~/.config/plasma-* | → ~/dotfiles/data/kde-plasma/.config/ | |
| ~/.config/programa | → ~/dotfiles/data/.config/programa | |

## Cadeia de links

_dev/dotfiles → ~/dotfiles
_dev/.agents → ~/.agents → ~/dotfiles/data/.agents/

Regra: qualquer alteração nestes symlinks altera o repositório de dotfiles e vice-versa.
